         MACRO
         LTT
***********************************************************************
*
*        DSECT FOR OVERLAYING AN ENTRY IN THE LINE AND TERMINAL
*        TABLE - LTT
*
***********************************************************************
         SPACE
LTT      DSECT
LTTENTDW DS    F   ENTRY DESCRIPTOR WORD - LENGTH OF THIS ENTRY
LTTIONME DS    CL8 NAME OF LINE I/O LOAD MODULE
LTTFTDCB DS    F   FORWARD POINTER OF TDCB CHAIN
LTTBTDCB DS    F   BACKWARD POINTER OF TDCB CHAIN
LTTIOTCB DS    F   LINE I/O TASK TCB ADDRESS
LTTENDEC DS    F   ECB POSTED BY OS WHEN LINE I/O TASK TERMINATES
LTTSPECB DS    F   POSTED BY LINE I/O FOR COMM TO SUPV
LTTLNECB DS    F   ECB POSTED BY SUPV FOR COMM. TO LINE I/O TASK
LTTDDNME DS    CL8 DDNAME USED TO ALLOCATE LINE UCB FOR LINE I/O
LTTRDRTE DS    CL8 LOAD MODULE NAME OF READ/WRITE ROUTINE
LTTCHK   DS    CL8 LOAD MODULE NAME OF CHECK ROUTINE
LTTTCNT  DS    H   COUNT OF TERMINALS ON THIS LINE
LTTBUFFL DS    H   SIZE OF 1ST TP BUFFR - MAX TP MSG SIZE
         DS    20F FOR EVERYTHING I FORGOT
*    THE FOLLOWING 'TRAILER' WILL OCCUR ONCE FOR EACH TERMINAL
LTTTYPE  DS    CL4 TERMINAL TYPE CODE
LTTSELID DS    XL4 BISYNC 'SELECT' ADDRESS OF TERMINAL
LTTPOLID DS    XL4 BISYNC 'POLL' ADDRESS OF TERMINAL
LTTMSGL  DS    H   BLKSIZE MINUS STX/ETX OF OUTBND MSGS
         DS    H
         DS    4F  FOR EVERYTHING I FORGOT
LTTEND   EQU   *
         MEND
